` component export and import, confirming correct usage within `LandingPage.tsx`. I'm now writing the logic for the video component, including simulated logs, a progress bar, and all related design elements.\nI'm ensuring the simulated video walkthrough logs stream properly, and am beginning to build the code.\n\n\n**Simulating Video Updates**\n\nI'm now integrating simulated real-time system logs within the video walkthrough, pulling data for dynamic display, as well as refining video player logic with states for `isPlaying` and `videoProgress`. I'm starting to build out a seamless animation loop and ensuring everything fits and displays well. I am still developing the simulated streaming video walkthrough.\n\n\n\n**Simulating Video Execution**\n\nI'm now focusing on simulating system execution within the video component. I'm adding simulated log lines to the video player component's states, and I'm developing the logic to dynamically display the log updates in the video. I've designed the animation loop and am ensuring the visual elements, including the simulated video, flow seamlessly. I'm actively working on the display logic for the simulated streaming video.\n\n\n**Refining Terminal Integration**\n\nI'm now integrating the simulated real-time system logs with a pulsing system flow diagram for the video player. I'm dynamically displaying logs within a scrolling terminal, ensuring synchronization with a spinning radar animation. The active log line index will be calculated to make them appear one by one, reflecting the progress of the video. The terminal should be perfectly synchronized to give the video premium detail.\n\n\n**Reviewing Section Code**\n\nI'm now writing and reviewing the code for `ClientSuccessSection.tsx`, ensuring error-free integration of the interactive video and architecture panel. I'm focusing on the component's state structure, making sure the `selectedPattern` and `activeNode` states are working correctly. I'll meticulously confirm that all required imports are included, while verifying that the design works, and that standard Tailwind colors are used.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:07:14.781Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"owvh97p1","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/ClientSuccessSection.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport SectionHeading from \"@/components/SectionHeading\";\n\n// Representative patterns data structure\ninterface PatternDetail {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  badge: string;\n  color: string;\n  textColor: string;\n  borderColor: string;\n  bgColor: string;\n  tagline: string;\n  description: string;\n  challenge: string;\n  solution: string;\n  outcomes: {\n    fasterDecisioning: string;\n    reducedManualEffort: string;\n    betterKnowledgeAccess: string;\n    improvedComplianceWorkflows: string;\n    improvedEmployeeExperience: string;\n  };\n  videoTitle: string;\n  videoDuration: string;\n}\n\nconst REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS: PatternDetail[] = [\n  {\n    id: \"banking\",\n    name: \"Global Banking\",\n    badge: \"REPRESENTATIVE PATTERN: FINANCIAL OPS\",\n    color: \"#009DFF\",\n    textColor: \"text-blue-400\",\n    borderColor: \"border-blue-500/20\",\n    bgColor: \"bg-blue-500/10\",\n    tagline: \"Multi-Agent Compliance & Algorithmic Risk Shield\",\n    description: \"A secure, modular multi-agent system deployed to automate cross-border auditing, KYC compliance reports, and transactional risk verification.\",\n    challenge: \"Parsing massive streams of global transaction data under constant structural changes in international financial reporting standards.\",\n    solution: \"A unified system of memory-equipped compliance agents checking multi-path transaction flows directly against state rulesets.\",\n    outcomes: {\n      fasterDecisioning: \"Accelerates high-volume trade audit and risk screening from several business days down to operational minutes.\",\n      reducedManualEffort: \"Automates complex, structured KYC reporting compilations, replacing laborious workbook documentation.\",\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Maintains a fully indexed, real-time semantic reference model of international monetary policies.\",\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Configures automated pre-audit screening gates that prevent structural AML compliance breaches.\",\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Frees forensic compliance officers from low-tier data checking to focus on complex anomaly investigations.\"\n    },\n    videoTitle: \"Financial Multi-Agent Auditing Walkthrough\",\n    videoDuration: \"01:45\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"healthcare\",\n    name: \"Healthcare Intel\",\n    badge: \"REPRESENTATIVE PATTERN: CLINICAL OPERATIONS\",\n    color: \"#E98828\",\n    textColor: \"text-orange-400\",\n    borderColor: \"border-orange-500/20\",\n    bgColor: \"bg-orange-500/10\",\n    tagline: \"Clinical Graph Orchestration & Patient Ingestion\",\n    description: \"A secure framework designed to unify clinical records, laboratory telemetry, and pharmaceutical research into an integrated real-time health graph.\",\n    challenge: \"Fragmented EHR data silos, mixed handwritten charts, and severe record inconsistency slowing patient profile compilation.\",\n    solution: \"Semantic pipeline extractors that parse multi-modal patient history records into a secure, HIPAA-compliant clinical knowledge layer.\",\n    outcomes: {\n      fasterDecisioning: \"Allows medical teams to access synthesized patient medical timelines instantly upon intake.\",\n      reducedManualEffort: \"Eliminated redundant manual transcription across records and patient health files.\",\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Synthesizes hospital clinical histories and medical journals into an aligned semantic index.\",\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Enforces continuous compliance audits with billing codes and patient safety standards.\",\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Greatly reduces clinician documentation fatigue, minimizing admin workloads.\"\n    },\n    videoTitle: \"Clinical Ingestion & Semantic Graph Overview\",\n    videoDuration: \"02:10\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"manufacturing\",\n    name: \"AI Factory\",\n    badge: \"REPRESENTATIVE PATTERN: INDUSTRIAL LOGISTICS\",\n    color: \"#E4000F\",\n    textColor: \"text-red-400\",\n    borderColor: \"border-red-500/20\",\n    bgColor: \"bg-red-500/10\",\n    tagline: \"Predictive Assembly & Telemetry Agent Grid\",\n    description: \"Bridging high-frequency physical assembly IoT networks with proactive, agentic maintenance and material supply-chain routing.\",\n    challenge: \"Unplanned physical machinery breakdowns and rigid supply line schedules that trigger expensive manufacturing downtime.\",\n    solution: \"Continuous telemetry parsing combined with predictive analysis agents that automatically plan physical system interventions.\",\n    outcomes: {\n      fasterDecisioning: \"Translates sensor threshold variations into early-warning maintenance flags hours before a malfunction.\",\n      reducedManualEffort: \"Automates machine work order creation and schedules preventative engineering workflows.\",\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Indexes real-time machinery telemetry histories, parts manuals, and historical repairs into an interactive dashboard.\",\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Maintains rigorous compliance with industrial safety regulations and environmental profiles.\",\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Replaces high-stress reactive troubleshooting with planned predictive maintenance routines.\"\n    },\n    videoTitle: \"IoT Telemetry Analysis & Preventative Pipeline\",\n    videoDuration: \"01:30\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"retail\",\n    name: \"Retail Agents\",\n    badge: \"REPRESENTATIVE PATTERN: CUSTOMER COMMERCE\",\n    color: \"#10B981\",\n    textColor: \"text-emerald-400\",\n    borderColor: \"border-emerald-500/20\",\n    bgColor: \"bg-emerald-500/10\",\n    tagline: \"Contextual Commerce Copilots & Inventory Orchestration\",\n    description: \"A unified cognitive system routing support enquiries, processing return policies, and optimizing omnichannel delivery networks.\",\n    challenge: \"High churn rates from delayed customer service answers and disconnected real-time inventory tracking systems.\",\n    solution: \"Conversational retail agents directly connected to localized stock indices and carrier status gateways.\",\n    outcomes: {\n      fasterDecisioning: \"Instantly resolves complex shipping adjustments and return calculations at the gateway.\",\n      reducedManualEffort: \"Safely automates repetitive support tickets and basic order adjustments without manual queuing.\",\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Provides immediate query access to thousands of product specifications and warranty parameters.\",\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Automatically reviews returns against localized consumer rights and store policies.\",\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Lifts repetitive inquiry burdens, allowing service personnel to focus on high-touch assistance.\"\n    },\n    videoTitle: \"Conversational Agent & Inventory Broker Walkthrough\",\n    videoDuration: \"01:55\"\n  }\n];\n\nconst NODES_DATA = [\n  [\n    { name: \"Audit Ingestion\", desc: \"Decodes SWIFT & ISO 20022 message blocks in real-time.\", tech: \"gRPC, Kafka, TLS 1.3\", status: \"INGESTING\" },\n    { name: \"Heuristic Compliance\", desc: \"Checks financial transactions against international compliance rules.\", tech: \"GFF Router, vLLM\", status: \"AUDITING\" },\n    { name: \"Secure Context Ledger\", desc: \"Maintains temporal patterns and KYC data in absolute isolation.\", tech: \"pgvector, Redis\", status: \"SECURED\" },\n    { name: \"Alert Gateway\", desc: \"Publishes SEC-compliant audit trails and anomaly notifications.\", tech: \"K8s, Temporal\", status: \"DISPATCHING\" },\n  ],\n  [\n    { name: \"Multi-Source EHR\", desc: \"Ingests FHIR structures, HL7 nodes, and patient PDFs.\", tech: \"Apache NiFi, S3\", status: \"CONNECTED\" },\n    { name: \"Semantic Extractor\", desc: \"Identifies clinical keywords and maps them to medical ontologies.\", tech: \"Llama-Index, Custom NER\", status: \"EXTRACTING\" },\n    { name: \"Clinical Knowledge Graph\", desc: \"Connects patient timelines and therapeutic relationships.\", tech: \"Neo4j, pgvector\", status: \"INDEXED\" },\n    { name: \"Care Coordinator Hub\", desc: \"Prepares verified diagnostic documentation summaries.\", tech: \"Temporal, Webhooks\", status: \"SYNTHESIZING\" },\n  ],\n  [\n    { name: \"IoT Telemetry Intake\", desc: \"Gathers PLC sensor points from active factory assembly networks.\", tech: \"MQTT, Apache Flink\", status: \"STREAMING\" },\n    { name: \"Anomaly Evaluator\", desc: \"Applies real-time mathematical safety thresholds across sensor points.\", tech: \"Python Core, Rust-WASM\", status: \"ANALYST ACTIVE\" },\n    { name: \"Equipment State Graph\", desc: \"Models component structures and historical machine parameters.\", tech: \"Neo4j, Redis\", status: \"MAPPED\" },\n    { name: \"Action Orchestrator\", desc: \"Triggers technician dispatches and schedules parts replacement.\", tech: \"K8s, ERP Gateway\", status: \"TRIGGER READY\" },\n  ],\n  [\n    { name: \"Omnichannel Intake\", desc: \"Aggregates incoming customer chats, emails, and ticket details.\", tech: \"Kafka, WebSocket\", status: \"LISTENING\" },\n    { name: \"Commerce Broker\", desc: \"Identifies user intention, order histories, and purchase variables.\", tech: \"GFF Core, LangGraph\", status: \"ROUTING\" },\n    { name: \"Inventory Vector Mesh\", desc: \"Scans real-time warehouse indexes and shipment paths.\", tech: \"pgvector, Neo4j\", status: \"QUERYING\" },\n    { name: \"Dispatch Gateway\", desc: \"Automates tracking coordinates and calculates return approvals.\", tech: \"Temporal, Stripe API\", status: \"FULFILLING\" },\n  ],\n];\n\nconst SIMULATED_LOGS = [\n  [\n    \"[INGEST-GATEWAY] listening on port 443 (gRPC/TLS 1.3)\",\n    \"[INGEST-GATEWAY] SWIFT packet detected. Decoding ISO 20022 XML payload...\",\n    \"[COMPLIANCE-ROUTER] packet structural verification: PASSED\",\n    \"[COMPLIANCE-ROUTER] scanning transaction routes against global KYC standards...\",\n    \"[MEMORY-MESH] searching relational ledger: pgvector match confidence 0.995\",\n    \"[MEMORY-MESH] historical transaction parameters loaded in 3.8ms\",\n    \"[COMPLIANCE-ROUTER] audit complete. Zero compliance anomalies found.\",\n    \"[OUTBOUND-GATEWAY] preparing signed compliance log export...\",\n    \"[OUTBOUND-GATEWAY] secure audit trace recorded and broadcasted.\"\n  ],\n  [\n    \"[EHR-GATEWAY] patient data queue initialized. Validating clinical feed...\",\n    \"[EHR-GATEWAY] multi-modal intake: parsing unstructured patient summary PDF...\",\n    \"[SEMT-ROUTER] running clinical entity extraction neural models...\",\n    \"[SEMT-ROUTER] parsed tags: [Type-II Diabetes, Metformin, HbA1c: 7.2%]\",\n    \"[CLINICAL-GRAPH] querying clinical relationship connections in Neo4j database...\",\n    \"[CLINICAL-GRAPH] patient health timeline parsed and linked.\",\n    \"[ACTION-HUB] drafting care-coordinator diagnostic clinical summary...\",\n    \"[ACTION-HUB] safe storage sync complete. HIPAA-compliant lock initialized.\"\n  ],\n  [\n    \"[IOT-GATEWAY] MQTT listener configured. Active on manufacturing-floor-5...\",\n    \"[IOT-GATEWAY] PLC frame ingested. Vibration: 2.1mm/s, Temperature: 82C\",\n    \"[ANALYST-ROUTER] running real-time statistical degradation safety check...\",\n    \"[ANALYST-ROUTER] warning: high-frequency vibration threshold crossed on shaft-H1\",\n    \"[EQUIP-GRAPH] querying structural equipment tree in Neo4j catalog...\",\n    \"[EQUIP-GRAPH] downstream risk profile computed: critical bearing fatigue predicted\",\n    \"[PREV-ENGINE] generating automated maintenance repair dispatch ticket...\",\n    \"[PREV-ENGINE] verified spare parts stock. Technician callout dispatched.\"\n  ],\n  [\n    \"[OMNI-HANDLER] webhook triggered: processing support ticket #9201a\",\n    \"[OMNI-HANDLER] tracking history parsed. Order: #81920-F, Segment: VIP Tier\",\n    \"[COMMERCE-ROUTER] parsing intention: shipment tracking and returns request...\",\n    \"[COMMERCE-ROUTER] querying live carrier API and transit nodes...\",\n    \"[INVENTORY-GRAPH] finding alternative warehouse product stock via pgvector...\",\n    \"[DISPATCH-BROKER] applying automated regional refund policy guidelines...\",\n    \"[DISPATCH-BROKER] return tracking label generated. Support workspace updated.\"\n  ]\n];\n\nexport default function ClientSuccessSection() {\n  const [selectedPattern, setSelectedPattern] = useState<number>(0);\n  const [activeNode, setActiveNode] = useState<number>(1);\n  const [isPlaying, setIsPlaying] = useState<boolean>(true);\n  const [videoProgress, setVideoProgress] = useState<number>(15);\n  const [visibleLogs, setVisibleLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);\n\n  const pattern = REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS[selectedPattern];\n  const activeNodes = NODES_DATA[selectedPattern];\n  const activeLogs = SIMULATED_LOGS[selectedPattern];\n  const activeColor = pattern.color;\n\n  // Sync video simulation\n  useEffect(() => {\n    let interval: NodeJS.Timeout | null = null;\n    if (isPlaying) {\n      interval = setInterval(() => {\n        setVideoProgress((prev) => {\n          const next = prev + 1;\n          return next > 100 ? 0 : next;\n        });\n      }, 150);\n    }\n    return () => {\n      if (interval) clearInterval(interval);\n    };\n  }, [isPlaying]);\n\n  // Sync log printing according to playback progress\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const totalLines = activeLogs.length;\n    const linesToShow = Math.floor((videoProgress / 100) * totalLines) + 1;\n    const cappedLines = Math.min(linesToShow, totalLines);\n    setVisibleLogs(activeLogs.slice(0, cappedLines));\n  }, [videoProgress, selectedPattern, activeLogs]);\n\n  // Handle active pattern change\n  const handlePatternChange = (idx: number) => {\n    setSelectedPattern(idx);\n    setActiveNode(1);\n    setVideoProgress(15);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <motion.section \n      id=\"client-success\"\n      initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n      whileInView={{ opacity: 1 }}\n      viewport={{ once: true }}\n      transition={{ duration: 1 }}\n      className=\"w-full bg-[#020202] px-6 lg:px-16 lg:py-32 py-20 relative overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5\"\n    >\n      {/* Abstract Background Accents */}\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style={{ backgroundImage: \"radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #E9882803 0%, transparent 50%)\" }} />\n      <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/5 to-transparent\" />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto relative z-10\">\n        \n        {/* Header Block */}\n        <div className=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <SectionHeading\n            title={\n              <h2 className=\"text-[32px] sm:text-[44px] leading-none font-bold text-center uppercase text-white tracking-widest\">\n                CLIENT <span className=\"text-[#E98828]\">SUCCESS</span>\n              </h2>\n            }\n            titleClassName=\"text-center\"\n            dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[300px]\"\n          />\n          <p className=\"mt-6 text-center text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#A0A0A0] max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed\">\n            We don't deploy static software or hypothetical sandboxes. We forge high-fidelity digital systems. Explore the system blueprints and outcomes behind our verified representative patterns.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* 1. Category Navigation - Representative Patterns Selector */}\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mb-16\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#E98828] font-bold\">\n            Select Representative System Pattern\n          </span>\n          <div className=\"w-full max-w-4xl bg-[#090909] border border-white/5 p-1.5 rounded-[16px] overflow-x-auto scrollbar-none flex gap-2 md:grid md:grid-cols-4\">\n            {REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS.map((p, idx) => {\n              const isSelected = selectedPattern === idx;\n              return (\n                <button\n                  key={p.id}\n                  onClick={() => handlePatternChange(idx)}\n                  className={`relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-3.5 px-4 rounded-[12px] transition-all duration-300 min-w-[170px] md:min-w-0 cursor-pointer ${\n                    isSelected \n                      ? \"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]\" \n                      : \"border border-transparent hover:bg-white/2 hover:border-white/5\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\">\n                    <span \n                      className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ${\n                        isSelected ? \"scale-110\" : \"opacity-30\"\n                      }`} \n                      style={{ backgroundColor: p.color, boxShadow: isSelected ? `0 0 8px ${p.color}` : 'none' }}\n                    />\n                    <span className={`text-[13px] font-bold tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300 ${isSelected ? \"text-white\" : \"text-white/50\"}`}>\n                      {p.name}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white/30 text-center block\">\n                    {idx === 0 ? \"Finance\" : idx === 1 ? \"Clinical\" : idx === 2 ? \"Industrial\" : \"Commerce\"}\n                  </span>\n                </button>\n              );\n            })}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* 2. Main Terminal Workspace */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-stretch\">\n          \n          {/* LEFT SIDE: Architecture & Video Simulation (Technical Layer) */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-6\">\n            \n            {/* Component Header Status */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border border-white/5 bg-[#050505] rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-[11px] font-mono tracking-wider text-white/40\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full ${isPlaying ? \"animate-pulse\" : \"\"}`} style={{ backgroundColor: activeColor, boxShadow: isPlaying ? `0 0 6px ${activeColor}` : 'none' }} />\n                <span className=\"text-white/70 uppercase font-bold\">SYSTEM STATE:</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white/80 font-bold font-mono uppercase\">\n                  {isPlaying ? \"REPRESENTATIVE SIMULATION ACTIVE\" : \"SIMULATION PAUSED\"}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span>SPEED:</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white/80 font-bold font-mono\">1.0x (SECURE)</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Architecture Preview Panel */}\n            <div className=\"w-full rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-[12px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 relative overflow-hidden\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border-l border-b border-white/5 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/40 rounded-bl-lg uppercase\">\n                Architecture Preview Panel\n              </div>\n              \n              <div>\n                <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-white/50 bg-white/5 rounded-md uppercase tracking-widest\">\n                  Blueprint Topology\n                </span>\n                <h4 className=\"mt-2 text-[18px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight uppercase\">\n                  System Architecture Flows\n                </h4>\n                <p className=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-[#A0A0A0] font-light\">\n                  Click on any architectural pipeline segment to inspect real-time system telemetry and engineering configurations.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Connected Pipeline Flow Visualizer */}\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-stretch relative my-4\">\n                {activeNodes.map((node, i) => {\n                  const isActive = activeNode === i;\n                  return (\n                    <button\n                      key={node.name}\n                      onClick={() => setActiveNode(i)}\n                      className={`text-left rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300 relative border cursor-pointer flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[110px] ${\n                        isActive\n                          ? \"bg-[#0A0A0A] shadow-lg\"\n                          : \"bg-black/20 border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-black/40\"\n                      }`}\n                      style={{ \n                        borderColor: isActive ? activeColor : \"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)\",\n                        boxShadow: isActive ? `0 0 16px ${activeColor}0f` : \"none\"\n                      }}\n                    >\n                      {/* Interactive indicator dot */}\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-2 w-full\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 font-bold\">0{i+1}</span>\n                        <span className=\"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-[4px] bg-white/5 text-[8px] font-mono font-bold\" style={{ color: activeColor }}>\n                          {node.status}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <h5 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white tracking-wide leading-tight mt-1\">\n                        {node.name}\n                      </h5>\n                    </button>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Node Inspector Panel */}\n              <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-5 mt-2\">\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start\">\n                  <div className=\"md:col-span-8\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/30 tracking-wider\">\n                      Selected Node Parameters\n                    </span>\n                    <h5 className=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-white mt-0.5\">\n                      {activeNodes[activeNode].name}\n                    </h5>\n                    <p className=\"text-[13px] text-[#808080] mt-1.5 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n                      {activeNodes[activeNode].desc}\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-3 border-l border-white/5 md:pl-4\">\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/30 tracking-wider block\">\n                        Engineered With\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"mt-1 inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/70\">\n                        {activeNodes[activeNode].tech}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Video walkthrough Simulator Component */}\n            <div className=\"w-full rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 overfl